Bradley Brandon (amụrụ n'ubochí mbụ n'ọnwa Septemba, n'afọ 1989), onye a maara dị ka Doughboy Beatz ma ọ bụ naanị Doughboy, bụ onye na-emepụta ihe ndekọ America si Columbus, Mississippi. O nwere ike ịbụ na a maara ya nke ọma maka imepụta "Pedestrian" site n'aka onye na-eti egwu Gunna, yana "Lost It" site n'aka onye na-eti egwu Rich The Kid gosipụtara Offset na Quavo nke Migos nke RIAA kwadoro ọla edo.

Doughboy emepụtala ụfọdụ egwu maka ndị egwu dị iche iche dịka Young Jeezy, Gucci Mane, Future, Yo Gotti, Juicy J, 21 Savage, NBA Youngboy, Lil Boosie, Soulja Boy, Shy Glizzy, YFN Lucci, Plies, Trina, Crooked I, B.G, CyHi the Prynce, n'etiti ndị ọzọ. O nwetara Grammy Nomination n'ihe banyere ọrụ ya na 21 Savage's I Am > I Was for Best Rap Album na 62nd Annual Grammy Awards.

Brandon bịdọrọ ịkụ egwu ógè ọ dị afọ iri na ise, maka nwanne ya nwoke nke nta na FL Studio. Ọ gara n'ihu mepụta Hitz Committee / Jive Records signee, Trai'D's lead single "Gutta Chick" na 2008. "Gutta Chick" ruru ọnụ ọgụgụ 72 na chaatị Billboard Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs.  Doughboy esorola ọtụtụ ndị ọzọ na-ese ihe kemgbe ahụ.

N'ime afọ 2010, Doughboy agbasoola mmepụta na ụfọdụ ọrụ a ma ama nke gụnyere Jeezy's Trap or Die 2, Shy Glizzy's Law 3, Rich The Kid's The World Is Yours, Gunna's Drip Season 3 na Gucci Mane's East Atlanta Santa
N'ọnwa Septemba n'afọ 2019, Doughboy bịanyere aka na Metro Boomin's Boominati Worldwide label.   Boominati Worldwide nwere mmekorita ya na Republic Records na Universal Music Group.
